long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly extract data from the search of real estate listings on Compass.com. It enables you to search properties and extract Compass data such as full addresses, price, description, URL, photos, number of bedrooms and bathrooms, and other available information to Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the compass list search page.
2️⃣ Perform a search, then click the "Start" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.
4️⃣ Find Our other powerful tools.

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by compass❗️🔒
